{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7cc7cc25-4ef7-467a-9766-09fc4b085a8d",
    "name": "Course Marketplace Backend API",
    "description": "Importable Postman Collection for the Course Marketplace Backend.\n\nThis collection is organized by backend module and is intended to stay in sync with implementation progress. It includes a built-in guide for auth, module responsibilities, response shape, and common usage flows.\n\nResponse envelope:\n- success: boolean\n- message: string\n- data: object | array | null\n- meta: optional pagination metadata\n\nAuth model:\n- Signup verification uses OTP routes under /api/v1/auth/*\n- Protected endpoints depend on the Better Auth session cookie created by /api/auth/* routes\n- Use Postman cookie persistence or run requests from the same collection tab/workspace\n\nImplemented modules in this version:\n- Health\n- Auth guidance with OTP verification and Better Auth session routes\n- Users\n- Course Categories\n- Courses\n\nPlanned future modules to append into this same collection:\n- Lessons\n- Enrollments\n- Payments\n- Reviews\n- Admin",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiPrefix",
      "value": "/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "categoryId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
